Package: CrownScorchTLS
Type: Package
Title: Estimate Crown Scorch from Terrestrial LiDAR Scans
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c( person("Jeffery", "Cannon", email =
        "Jeffery.Cannon@jonesctr.org", role = c("aut","cre")),
        person("Andrew", "Whelan", role = "ctb") )
Description: Estimates tree crown scorch from terrestrial lidar scans
        collected with a RIEGL vz400i. The methods follow those
        described in Cannon et al. (2025, Fire Ecology 21:71,
        <doi:10.1186/s42408-025-00420-0>).
